Package: bright-iputils
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: BrightDate/BrightSpace networking tools (bping, bclockdiff, btraceroute, bmtr, baudit)
 Bright iputils is a BrightDate/BrightSpace-ready fork of iputils, providing
 modernized versions of classic Linux networking tools with a universal,
 timezone-free time system. All tools output and accept BrightDate scalars
 for timestamps and are designed for BrightSpace (spatial) and Bright
 Spacetime (4D) extensions.
 .
 Included tools (b-prefixed to coexist with system iputils):
  * bping    — BrightDate/BrightSpace ping
  * bclockdiff — BrightDate/BrightSpace clock difference
  * btraceroute — BrightDate/BrightSpace traceroute
  * bmtr     — BrightDate/BrightSpace MTR-style tool
  * baudit   — BrightDate network audit tool
